    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>如果你遇到任何错误或想要分享反馈，欢迎加入我们的Discord频道。我们很乐意听取你对试玩版的想法，以便我们让游戏变得更加出色！</i> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >试玩版内容概览： </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在试玩版中体验到的内容只是完整版游戏的一小部分。在20-30分钟的游戏过程中，你将能够感受到《Chorus of Carcosa》的整体氛围。你将尝试一些游戏机制，还会遇到几位“诡异之屋”的住客。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，游戏内容仍在开发中，后续会添加更多内容。《Chorus of Carcosa》计划于明年发布。疯狂之门即将开启……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.webp?t=1740066554\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.poster.avif?t=1740066554\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=33 /></picture></span>沉浸在神秘和疯狂的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Chorus of Carcosa》是一款单人心理恐怖游戏。游戏讲述了一位焦虑的独居雕塑家，某个深夜，浑身是血的邻居敲响了他的门，从此他被迫离开舒适的住所。故事灵感源于罗伯特·W·钱伯斯的经典恐怖故事集《黄衣之王》，创作团队将其中堕入疯狂的体验改编成了第一人称生存游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/f9e26acaddc54a952a5f73765c0cb76c.poster.avif?t=1740066554\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/f9e26acaddc54a952a5f73765c0cb76c.webm?t=1740066554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/f9e26acaddc54a952a5f73765c0cb76c.mp4?t=1740066554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验面对未知的恐惧</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一栋千变万化的老式公寓楼中生存下来，楼中危机重重、神秘莫测。克服令人麻痹的恐惧和精神错乱，逃离未知的神秘怪物和疯狂的邻居。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/05c95659de16d850bb38467242a5dc8c.poster.avif?t=1740066554\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/05c95659de16d850bb38467242a5dc8c.webm?t=1740066554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/05c95659de16d850bb38467242a5dc8c.mp4?t=1740066554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解开交替现实的谜团</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验“卡尔克萨”，一个可以侵入你周围空间的交替现实。所有这些变化都是真实的吗？还是仅仅是噩梦般的幻觉？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/95c849dd83c35a30cfbf8ad338b61507.poster.avif?t=1740066554\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/95c849dd83c35a30cfbf8ad338b61507.webm?t=1740066554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/95c849dd83c35a30cfbf8ad338b61507.mp4?t=1740066554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感受这个奇异的反乌托邦世界，沉浸在令人毛骨悚然的氛围中</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进由虚幻引擎5精心打造的怪诞建筑，沉浸在阴森恐怖的迷宫中。逼真的画面和优质的3D环绕音效，将让你沉浸在令人窒息的恐惧氛围中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/7590e67eda235f84d8fc19a0a28cf3e1.poster.avif?t=1740066554\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/7590e67eda235f84d8fc19a0a28cf3e1.webm?t=1740066554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/7590e67eda235f84d8fc19a0a28cf3e1.mp4?t=1740066554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.webp?t=1740066554\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297830/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.poster.avif?t=1740066554\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=33 /></picture></span></p>",
